Do not restart from scratch.
Do not remove existing working features unless explicitly instructed.
Treat the objective delta as additive unless it clearly says replacement.
`;
  }

  return `
PASS MODE:
This is an initial creation pass.
Create the first complete product foundation.
Establish stable structure, names, sections, selectors, metadata, and interaction surfaces for later lanes and future passes.
`;
}

